Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(178,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2C3995&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara escaped GOD and tore the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to entrust to his old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has stolen one of the pieces,\Nand the X Rider holds two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus does a deadly race for the\Nremaining six pieces begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellish Dictator\NStarfish Hitler!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\i1}Tokyo International Airport\NInternational Departures{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, the fourth blueprint\Npiece is here from America...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this Dr. Egawa's the\Nbiggest physicist in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok chief, let's put the plan into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Time to do our thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Welcome!\N-Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you Dr. Egawa from\Nthe United College of Technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take you to the\Nhotel for the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The car's ready, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They totally blanked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? And after we were so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be Chiko and Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you, Dr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Starfish Hitler,\Nof GOD's Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My secret police identified you, a student of Dr.\NNanbara, as having received a blueprint in the USA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're going to take you\Nsomewhere more comfortable. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, we were right. Those\Njournalists are with GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! I'm on their tail now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Führer! There's a motorbike after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Jin Keisuke, is it?\NNever mind, keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The mic's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor must've...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, try to track our scientist\Ncouple by their mic's wavelength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark, may I introduce the United College\Nof Technology's Dr. Egawa and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from the\Nevil dictator Starfish Hitler...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what I'd like to be saying, you fool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not Dr. Egawa or his wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They obviously changed places\Nwith these impostors in America!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find the genuine article!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me that blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you'd rather be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O-of course, sir! I shan't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke's substitution plan\Nworked great, didn't it, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it sure did. But the doctor\Nand his wife must be exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! It was almost fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But will our two impostors be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, Keisuke's gone after them.\N-They'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More voltage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Release her. We don't want her dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you feel like talking yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the reincarnation of Hitler, whose\Ncruelty caused the world to tremble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have ways of making you talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just hippies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is that I was asked\Nto stand in for Dr. Egawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How bold you are, daring to challenge GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we should run if you\Nfound out! That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... betray them! How could\Nyou... live with yourself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Do you want to die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just answer one question:\NWhere is the real Dr. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know all the details, but he's\Nhiding somewhere at the Manazuru coast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Manazuru coast, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed Jin Keisuke! He's found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A starfish in a tree...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, GOD monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am the hellish dictator of\NGOD\N's Villain Army: Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, X Rider. But I haven't\Nthe time to waste with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Where's the couple you\Nkidnapped from the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for you to figure out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't budge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Electric Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like an entrance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"X Rider, your trick was a daring one. I will certainly repay you in kind."\N--Starfish Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, it's been so long\Nsince we relaxed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe taking the odd sunbathing\Nbreak from research isn't too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's enough to make you forget about GOD!\N-But... should we be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're not just lazing\Naround! We're hiding from GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of... The blueprint's safe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! It's in there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found them... and this time\Nthey won't fool us! Begin offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Room service!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the Egawas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-They went to their room for dinner.\N-Oh, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of GOD yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Keisuke's kind of late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up. There was a time bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, are the Egawas safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're fine. Just\Nwent back to their room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our two impostors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in hospital, critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-At least they're alive...\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a day... Let's make the most of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-To our health!\N-Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... Shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the starfish--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of GOD's monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right! I am the hellish dictator of\NGOD\N's Villain Army: Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your knowledge of us makes things\Nsimpler. Give me the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a persistent one, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over that bracelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-You alright?\N-The blueprint is ours. Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hold it!!\N-Keisuke, you can't fight in your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... chief, please let me go! Who\Nknows what might happen if they get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Alright. But I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want more, X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Starfish Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitz Starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that feel, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler's finishing move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whirling Hell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!! Don't lose! You can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider... I won't let you\Nget this blueprint piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It will... explode with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish... Hitler...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The bracelet with the blueprint...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief...\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've got three... But\Nwe have to find the other six!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider narrowly brought down\Nthe hellish dictator Starfish Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Dark won't stop\Nthere. What's coming next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next week is a Kamen Rider Special Edition\Nfeaturing Kamen Riders #1, #2, V3, Riderman, and X...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...in mortal combat with the monsters of\NShocker, GelShocker and Deathtron!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Special Edition - The 5 Riders in Full Force!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider